In [51]:
def main(data,b):
    q1 = np.percentile(data[b],25)
    q2 = np.percentile(data[b],50)
    q3 = np.percentile(data[b],75)
    iqr = q3 - q1
    lower_fence = q1 - (iqr*1.5)
    upper_fence = q3 +  (iqr*1.5)
    lower_fence,upper_fence
    data[b] = np.where(((data[b]<lower_fence)|(data[b]>upper_fence)),q2,data[b])
for i in ['pizza_id','order_id','quantity','unit_price','total_price','year','weekday']:
    main(data,i)
